45
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala što pratite kanal.

46
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Božja riječ stari zavijet.

47
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ta povijest je jako konkretna.

48
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači još nismo na razini duhovnog tumačenja.

49
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da je robstvo duhovna stvar.

50
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da je pravo robstvo čovjeka grijeh i tako dalje.

51
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je morao postepeno se objavljivati čovjeku.

52
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sa izraelskim narodom morao konkretno raditi iz jednog robstva u Egiptu.

53
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Poslije su došli.

54
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ova riječ zapravo govori o kontekstu je babilonsko sužanjstvo.

55
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon što su već imali hram.

56
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon što su već živjeli tamo.

57
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imali kulturu, pismo, vjeru, hram.

58
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svečenike, kralja.

59
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njihovo srce se odvratilo od gospodina.

60
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kako je bilo u ugovoru, u savezu.

61
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je uvijek rekao.

62
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] A kad vam se srce, kad mi više ne budete slušali.

63
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ću vas predati vašim neprijateljima.

64
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako se dogodilo.

65
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Došli su babilonci.

66
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pobili su koje su pobili.

67
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Većinu naroda su odveli.

68
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] ostale samo sirotinja tamo na toj zemlji.

69
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je ona riječ krotki će baštiniti zemlju.

70
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je sad druga tema.

71
00:03:56,000 --> 00:04:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Za puno toga je ključ u Svetom pismu i u Novom Zavijetu i onome što Isus govori babilonsko sužanjstvo.

72
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedno konkretno robstvo fizičko jednog naroda gdje su ih,

73
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedan drugi narod ih je porobio.

74
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bio običaj u to vrijeme.

75
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad porobiš jedan narod, odvedeš ih lijepo u kući.

76
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ti čuvaju, imaš besplatno babysitter,

77
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] imaš besplatno graditelje,

78
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] imaš besplatno učitelje,

79
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] školu, neko ko ti je on.

80
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Lijepo su ti robovi i to je to.

81
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ovaj narod u babilonskom služanstvu,

82
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] već desetljećima,

83
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] neki su možda zaboravili Jeruzalem,

84
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda su oni govorili,

85
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] nek mi se osuši desnica,

86
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] to jest neću svirat gitaru,

87
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu svirat,

88
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] nek mi se jezik prilijepi za nepce,

89
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] neću ni pjevat,

90
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] kaže,

91
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer mislim, jer mi je jedna tuga,

92
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] iznad svih mojih radostima,

93
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedna tuga, to je Čežnja za Jeruzalemom.

94
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su, vidimo, tri točke geografske,

95
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] koje mogu tebi pomoći da mapiraš,

96
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo, gdje si ti danas,

97
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je danas tvoja duša,

98
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je tvoja nutrina,

99
00:04:56,000 --> 00:05:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer jezik nutrine je uvijek neizreciv

100
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] nekim, ne znam, govorom egzaktnim,

101
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] zašto postoje umjetno,

102
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] zašto postoje poezija,

103
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] zašto postoje priče, bajke, mitovi,

104
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] prispodove, kriz koristi,

105
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] da bi se izrazilo ono što,

106
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] ovo neizrecivo što se događa u nutrini.

107
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, onda ima jedna,

108
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bože reči danas ti daje mapu,

109
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] da ti vidiš gdje si,

110
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] i da se možeš pomaknuti,

111
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] ako nisi na dobrom mjestu,

112
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] da možeš išći naprijed.

113
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su tri glavne geografska položaja,

114
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo, spomenuo sam već Babilon,

115
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] sužanjstvo, ropstvo,

116
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je situacija čovjekova,

117
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] ono za što je čovjek stvoren je Jeruzalem,

118
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo, da je svoj na svome,

119
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo, pokušao bi to objasniti šta to znači,

120
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo, jedna od značenja je da vlada sobom.

121
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je slatko, gorko je biti u ropstvu,

122
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] i slatko je kad vlada.

123
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] između te dvije,

124
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] ta geografska položaja,

125
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] nalazi se ogromna pustinjetina.

126
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] I čak kad bi nas ovi pustili da idemo,

127
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] to se je dogodilo kad je došao jedan kir,

128
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedan njihov kraj,

129
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] kada je pustio židovski narod da se vrati,

130
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo, beshrabren sam tako će sad kroz tu pustinju,

131
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] a i tu sam već sam se rodio,

132
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] tu Babilon i sam gradio kuću,

133
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] i snašao sam se i tako dalje,

134
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] ono su proroci došli o hrabrit narod.

135
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, vidimo kako ta usporedba

136
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] može nam pomoći što se događa u našoj nutrini.

137
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda vidi ti danas gdje si ti opita,

138
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] ova riječ te pita. Gdje si ti danas?

139
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi li u Babilonu?

140
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi li krenuo na put prema Jeruzalemu?

141
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili si se asimilirao u Babilonu i to je to, živiš?

142
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili si već u pustinji,

143
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] ide Bog za tobom,

144
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] vidiš kako miče prepreke, kako si na putu,

145
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako te Bog maknuje s tvoje statike,

146
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] gdje samo čekaš smrti, to je to.

147
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] I vidiš da nije sve jedno kako živiš, boriš se,

148
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je znak da jedan čovjek hoda prema Jeruzalemu,

149
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] je kajanjena.

150
00:06:57,000 --> 00:07:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Postoji čovjek koji je zaspao u Jeruzalemu,

151
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] u Babilonu, on se navikao na sve.

152
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa ga više ne,

153
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] samo ga uznamiruju možda tuđi grijesi,

154
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] a moji me više ne uznamiruju. To je tako, to tako treba biti.

155
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ono treba doći jedan glas istine,

156
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji mora vikat,

157
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je veličina Ivana, to je divota koji imamo,

158
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] znak u svoj tom pismu,

159
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] da Bog nije znao više što,

160
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako je bio ljut na narod, kako kaže,

161
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] doslovno kaže,

162
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Bog digao nos",

163
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] mi ne provodimo tako, ali kad se čita na hebrevski,

164
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Bog je digao nos".

165
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kad je Bog skroz digao nos,

166
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] i nije mogao,

167
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda kaže da više nije slao riječ,

168
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda su se oni tužili,

169
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako više, kaže, i proroci i svećenici

170
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] lutaju po zemlji i ništa ne znaju.

171
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako mnogi ljudi kažu,

172
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, tamo kod nas ništa,

173
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] sve suhoparno, svećenik ništa ne govori,

174
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] najviše ni propovedi, niše, evo,

175
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] nema više riječi,

176
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, evo, to ne ovisi samo svećeniku,

177
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] nego Bog da narodu,

178
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji hoće slušati, da, nekom ko hoće,

179
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] ko govori, i meni treba, svaki dan

180
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] govoriti, treba se izlagati

181
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] istini, jer znamo da je,

182
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo, da bi malo objasnili ovo ropstvo,

183
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] služanstvo koje mi živimo,

184
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] svjetimo se one Isusove riječi,

185
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] koja kaže, "Ostanite u mojoj riječi,

186
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] upoznat ćete istinu,

187
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] i istina će vas osloboditi."

188
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad možemo, šta će me osloboditi?

189
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su farizei, kada Isus govorio

190
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] o oslobodženju, oni su rekli, ma šta, nismo mi robovi.

191
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je čovjek koji živi u laži,

192
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji je otuđen,

193
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] i zato je došao jedan krstitelj, raskrinka to,

194
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] zato je vikao, prokazivao je grijehe,

195
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] nije se bojavao nikoga.

196
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hralju je govorio, svi znali,

197
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali svi su ono malo, evo,

198
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne talasaj, nemoj izgubiti glavu,

199
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] nemoj se zamjeriti, nemojte čas zamiriti,

200
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] kažu istri, evo, nemoj...

201
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bojimo se istine

202
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] i bojimo se jedni i drugih.

203
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog i svoje, revnoj ljubavi za nas,

204
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] upali ovaj oganj u srcu proroka.

205
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sjetite se, proroka Jeremija,

206
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] kojim se više nije dalo uopće govoriti,

207
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] rekao je: neću govoriti više u tvoje ime,

208
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer samo mi donosi probleme to,

209
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] žele me ubiti,

210
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] bacili su u jedan bunar,

211
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] tamo je bio Danima,

212
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali onda kaže: ali u mojim kostima

213
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] bio je zapreten oganj

214
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] i morao sam govoriti.

215
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je Božja ljubav i ja zahvaljujem Bogu

216
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] da danas, nakon 2000 godina,

217
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] nakon Ivana Krstitelja,

218
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] još uvijek u crkvi postoji,

219
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam gdje drugo,

220
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] postoji ovaj revnost da se meni,

221
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] da se tebi kaže istina.

222
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ima neke opće istine,

223
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, koje mi ne prihvaćamo.

224
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo sam ti ovo reći,

225
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] da ta rečenica koju Krist kaže

226
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] istina će vas osloboditi.

227
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta ona znači kad malo uđeš u nju?

228
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] To znači da smo mi u ropstvu,

229
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne zato što smo prisiljeni,

230
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] nego to je dobrovoljno ropstvo, jer želimo biti u njemu.

231
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] žele ostati u Babilonu.

232
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne vjeruju da tamo ima,

233
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je život,

234
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je čovjek koji gleda ponografiju

235
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ne želi izaći.

236
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi ljudi žele izaći.

237
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, pustiti, to je život.

238
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Potpuno izgubi dostojanstvo,

239
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] rob je, ne znam,

240
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] neko je rob gnjeva,

241
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:03,000
[UNKNOWN] neko je rob tuge,

242
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo možemo nabrojiti onih osam strasti.

243
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] vidiš da je to robstvo,

244
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] odozimati dostojanstvo.

245
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] U Nisi, stari su govorili,

246
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] slatko je vladati.

247
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] To svi možemo razumjeti kako je slatko,

248
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad imamo neku vlast.

249
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, obično, kad imaš neku vlast,

250
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] a svi smo grešnici pa ne radimo dobro tu vlast,

251
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda donosimo gorčinu drugima.

252
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda se on bori da on dođe na vlast,

253
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa i to svaku vlast onda ispuni gorčinom,

254
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali ima jedna vlast

255
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] koja je sama slatkoća.

256
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad imaš tu vlast,

257
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] nikoga ne ispunjaš gorčinom,

258
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] a u tebi je slatkoća.

259
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znate koja je to vlast?

260
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad imaš tu vlast,

261
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] nikoga ne ispunjaš gorčinom,

262
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] a u tebi je slatkoća.

263
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je kad imaš vlast nad samim sobom.

264
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda promisli koliko puta si neke ljude napunio gorčinom,

265
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer nisi vladao sobom.

266
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko, čovjek kada se preljubi,

267
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda gorčina u djeci,

268
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] u ženi koja je prevarana,

269
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] u mužu koja je prevarana,

270
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer čovjek nije vladao sobom.

271
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vladao neke emocije,

272
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] požuda,

273
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] bilo što.

274
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili srebroljublje vlada nama,

275
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] ili tuga vlada s nama.

276
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedino kad čovjek vlada sa sobom,

277
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne ispunja,

278
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, ponavljam više puta,

279
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer i meni to dira,

280
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedin da istina,

281
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne ispunjam druge gorčinom,

282
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] a u meni dolazi jedna slatkoća.

283
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Puno puta Bože reči govori o slatkoći.

284
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kriz kaže:

285
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moj Aram je sladak.

286
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda kaže,

287
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] psalam,

288
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] tvoje riječi su sladke,

289
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne pcu mome.

290
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neki nas smo na zornici čitali psalam

291
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je sladak.

292
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možda to nekom se čini nerealno,

293
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali želi reći da ovaj cilj,

294
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] dvije stvari prorok mora vikat.

295
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mora raskrenkavati grijeh,

296
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] mora raskrenkavati robstvo i govori čovjeku:

297
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Budalo!

298
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Živiš u robstvu,

299
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] probudi se,

300
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] makni se s te mrtve točke.

301
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto tamo sjediš u svom izmetu

302
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] i kažeš da ti je dobro,

303
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Budalo?

304
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je vikao Ivan Trsitelj,

305
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] o to vičem ja danas tebi.

306
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako te ne dira,

307
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] ako ideš u crkvu desetljećima,

308
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] nikad se nisi pukajao za grijehe,

309
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] nikad nisi naišao na ispovjed.

310
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže ovdje da su ispovjedali svoje grijehe.

311
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Govorili su ih.

312
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] To nije izmislila crkva u srednjem vijeku.

313
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je Bog nadahnu u izraelskom narodu.

314
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] već da to put izlječenja,

315
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] izgovori svoje grijehe.

316
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad čovjek ovog svijeta izgovara svoje grijehe,

317
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek izgovara tuđe.

318
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zato ostaje u robstvu.

319
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zato ostaje u tuzi.

320
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može upoznat slatkoću,

321
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer to je prva stvar,

322
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] raskrinka laži,

323
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] i druga stvar,

324
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] otkrit slatkoću koju možeš dobiti.

325
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možda neko misli da to da je Bog sladak,

326
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] ta rečenica mi odzvanja od kada smo neki nam čitali

327
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] u psalmu na Zornici,

328
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] možda kao neka pobožnjačka stvar.

329
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Padaju mi na pamet više primjera.

330
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sjetite se one crnkinje.

331
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stavio sam, molim vas pogledajte ako niste.

332
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Taj njezino iskustvo može promijeniti čovjek u život.

333
00:12:56,000 --> 00:13:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona crnkinja koja je bila, stavio sam tamo na moj kanal,

334
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] zove se Makjule ili Bažiza iz Ruande.

335
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Preživila je pokolj, ono WC u tamo,

336
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] sakrivala se mjesecima,

337
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] pobili svom sjelu obitelj.

338
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona u toj borbi,

339
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] unutarnjoj borbi koja je fantastično opisana,

340
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Boga je dao i dar da to dobro opiše,

341
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] da bi mi mogli prepoznat sebe.

342
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] U tome je odlučila se ić,

343
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] napustit svoj Babilon,

344
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] napustit svoje gnjev,

345
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] ropstvo gnjevu i slijedit Krista.

346
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je bila katolika,

347
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] išla je od Malena u crkvu,

348
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] čula je i ušima o tome,

349
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali poslije Bog.

350
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer kad je molila OČe Naš,

351
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] sjetite ko niste gledali,

352
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] toliko je bila ljuta ove ljude,

353
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] čula ih je tamo iza ormara,

354
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako se hvale,

355
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako su ubili stotine ljudi.

356
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta je ovo?

357
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se neko može hvali

358
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] da je ubio stotine ljudi?

359
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je došao gnjev da ih sve pobijede.

360
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kada je molila OČe Naš,

361
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] oprosti nam duge naše,

362
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda nije mogla,

363
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] preskakala je tu,

364
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] preskakala je taj dio,

365
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] nije mogla.

366
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bila je više u ropstvu,

367
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] nego u ropstvu od straha,

368
00:13:58,000 --> 00:14:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] bila je u ropstvu od gnjeva.

369
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže da vam se i tijelo mijenjalo,

370
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] da je glava bola,

371
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] i da je smrdila,

372
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] i da je kada smo u tim ropstvima,

373
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] čovjek je manje čovjek,

374
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad živimo gnjevo.

375
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda, ovo sam ti joj reći,

376
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] na kraju jer je išla za Kristom,

377
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] divno jezino iskustvo,

378
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] na divan način priča,

379
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] vidiš unutra,

380
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] bez osude prema ikome,

381
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] kaže kad je to sve prestalo,

382
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad je ona izašla,

383
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] već tamo imala velike utjehe,

384
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] već tamo kad je rekla

385
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] neću ostati u ovom izmetu gnjeva,

386
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] slijediću Krista,

387
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] slijediću moga Krista,

388
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] slijediću Boga,

389
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] slijediću Boga,

390
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne želim uvrijediti Krista,

391
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad kažem da je slon,

392
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo ova usporenda,

393
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] puno veći je,

394
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] nego što je od mene,

395
